# Hardware Components with Specifications

1. NodeMCU (ESP8266)

* Operating Voltage: 3.3V
* Input Voltage: 5V (via Vin/USB)
* Wi-Fi: 802.11 b/g/n
* GPIO Pins: 11 digital I/O
* ADC: 1 (0–3.3V)

2. Soil Moisture Sensor

* Operating Voltage: 3.3V–5V
* Output: Analog/Digital
* Function: Measures soil water content

3. DHT11 Temperature & Humidity Sensor

* Voltage: 3.3V–5V
* Temperature Range: 0–50°C
* Humidity Range: 20–80%
* Output: Digital

4. DS18B20 Temperature Sensor

* Voltage: 3.0V–5.5V
* Output: Digital (1-Wire)
* Accuracy: ±0.5°C

5. LDR (Light Dependent Resistor)

* Type: Analog sensor
* Function: Measures light intensity
* Used with voltage divider (10kΩ resistor)

6. Relay Module

* Voltage: 5V
* Type: Electromagnetic switch
* Function: Controls water pump

7. Water Pump (DC)

* Voltage: 12V DC
* Function: Irrigation control

8. TIP122 Transistor

* Type: NPN Darlington
* Function: Switching high-power devices

9. Voltage Regulator (7805)

* Input: 7V–12V
* Output: 5V regulated

10. Power Supply

* Input: 12V DC Adapter
